{"data":[{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:59:21+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":242216,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2020-09-18","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/52/7b/242216_kNqWl.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/52/7b/242216_kNqWl.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/52/7b/242216_kNqWl.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/52/7b/242216_kNqWl.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/52/7b/242216_kNqWl.jpg"},"name":"劇場版 ヴァイオレット・エヴァーガーデン","name_cn":"剧场版 紫罗兰永恒花园","summary":"从事代笔职业的她，名叫薇尔莉特·伊芙加登。在让人们伤痕累累的战争结束后数年，崭新的时代来临，世界也逐渐恢复平稳，生活也随着新技术的开发而改变，大家都在向前迈进。但是，薇尔莉特每天都在思念“那个人”，她坚信他一定还活着。直到某天，她在邮局的仓库里发现了一封收件人不明的信……","total_episodes":1,"eps":1},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:55:24+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":244761,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2020-02-29","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/12/f3/244761_tGK1D.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/12/f3/244761_tGK1D.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/12/f3/244761_tGK1D.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/12/f3/244761_tGK1D.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/12/f3/244761_tGK1D.jpg"},"name":"劇場版 SHIROBAKO","name_cn":"剧场版 白箱","summary":"总有一天不论如何都要一起制作动画——上山高中动画同好会的5人向葫芦屋的甜甜圈如此起誓。她们毕业以后，分别在各自的岗位从事动画制作，并通过《第三飞行少女队》而接近了自己的梦想。\r\n4年后——。在动画的世界找到了自己的容身之所、逐渐成长起来的5人，开始面对新的苦恼和试炼。","total_episodes":2,"eps":1},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:50:43+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":137722,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2016-01-07","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/39/2f/137722_Iid43.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/39/2f/137722_Iid43.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/39/2f/137722_Iid43.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/39/2f/137722_Iid43.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/39/2f/137722_Iid43.jpg"},"name":"僕だけがいない街","name_cn":"只有我不存在的城市","summary":"　　藤沼悟是一个三流漫画家，但是他却拥有着名为“再上映”（可以穿越到事件发生之前的时间点，阻止事件发生，但失败了会一直重复）的能力。某天，当回到家里的时候他发现了自己母亲遇害的一幕，并且自己被嫁祸为杀人凶手。就在这时候，由于再上映的关系，他突然回到了18年前·小学五年级的时候，而这一刻他不但要拯救母亲，也要为了同学的安全而战……","total_episodes":14,"eps":12},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:50:30+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":185943,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2017-04-11","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a0/5f/185943_VDh22.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a0/5f/185943_VDh22.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a0/5f/185943_VDh22.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a0/5f/185943_VDh22.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a0/5f/185943_VDh22.jpg"},"name":"終末なにしてますか？ 忙しいですか？ 救ってもらっていいですか？","name_cn":"末日时在做什么？有没有空？可以来拯救吗？","summary":"       被称作妖精兵器的少女们与残存的准勇者之间的虚幻而痛切的物语。\r\n       地上遭到正体不明的怪物“兽”的蹂躏，包括人类在内的多种族被毁灭之后的世界。\r\n       勉强残存的种族离开地面，移居到名为浮游大陆群（Regulu Ere）的空中群岛上生活。\r\n       在500年后的空中醒来的威廉·克梅修，在无法守护自己本欲守护之物，甚至仅剩自己一人的绝望之中度过着与世隔绝的生活，但在出乎意料地开展的兵器管理工作当中，他与少女们相遇了。","total_episodes":12,"eps":12},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:50:11+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":266301,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2020-01-12","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/8c/2b/266301_1A1qq.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/8c/2b/266301_1A1qq.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/8c/2b/266301_1A1qq.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8c/2b/266301_1A1qq.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/8c/2b/266301_1A1qq.jpg"},"name":"ドロヘドロ","name_cn":"异兽魔都","summary":"欢迎光临，混沌。\r\n被魔法作用下头部变成了蜥蜴同时也完全丧失了记忆的男子·开曼。\r\n开曼为了变回人脸和找回记忆，和搭档的二阶堂一起在寻找着给自己下了这个魔法的魔法师。\r\n自己到底是谁……","total_episodes":13,"eps":12},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:48:01+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":334,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2002-01-15","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/2f/2b/334_MWQMC.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/2f/2b/334_MWQMC.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/2f/2b/334_MWQMC.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/2f/2b/334_MWQMC.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/2f/2b/334_MWQMC.jpg"},"name":"フルメタル・パニック!","name_cn":"全金属狂潮","summary":"在20世纪，世界格局比较稳定的时候，各大国都想增强自己的军事力量，从而称霸世界。而Whisper[耳语者]这种特殊的人类，自从出生开始就拥有特殊的能力，不用学习也能知道超越当时科技几十年的被称为黑科技的高科技手段。为了保护世界格局的稳定，神秘组织Mithril[米斯利尔]派出了相良中士等三人去保护一名已知的Whisper[耳语者]，即千鸟香奈。其中相良中士装成转校生随时跟踪保护，由于长期处于军队的生活，完全没有普通高中生的生活常识的相良中士在学校里闹了不少笑话。在学校期间也发生了不少恐怖的事情，如苏联为绑架香奈制造的劫机事件等。宗介和千鸟之间也因为发生的各种事件产生了特殊的感情。","total_episodes":24,"eps":24},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:45:12+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":90880,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2014-04-26","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/59/8d/90880_NYUDd.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/59/8d/90880_NYUDd.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/59/8d/90880_NYUDd.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/59/8d/90880_NYUDd.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/59/8d/90880_NYUDd.jpg"},"name":"たまこラブストーリー","name_cn":"玉子爱情故事","summary":"时已入春，已经进入高中三年级的北白川玉子仍然总是想着打糕的事情。\r\n春天傍晚的放学路上，玉子好友四人组谈论着关于将来出路的事情。大家虽然对此感到不安，但似乎对将来的事情都有好好地考虑过。玉子也无意中说出自己将来想要继承家业。\r\n同时，住在玉子家的对面、一直和她在一起的饼藏，也下定了某种决心。\r\n周围的各种事物都在逐渐改变着，一点一点地动摇着玉子的心。","total_episodes":1,"eps":1},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:41:05+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":3995,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2008-09-06","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/d4/64/3995_Y2SXy.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/d4/64/3995_Y2SXy.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/d4/64/3995_Y2SXy.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/d4/64/3995_Y2SXy.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/d4/64/3995_Y2SXy.jpg"},"name":"劇場版 天元突破グレンラガン 紅蓮篇","name_cn":"天元突破红莲螺岩 红莲篇","summary":"剧场版第1部。2008年9月6日上映。主要剧情为TV第1-14话的总集编，并对大红莲团对战四天王的部分进行了重新演绎。","total_episodes":1,"eps":1},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:38:10+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":211311,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2018-01-05","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c2/c7/211311_778A7.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c2/c7/211311_778A7.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c2/c7/211311_778A7.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c2/c7/211311_778A7.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c2/c7/211311_778A7.jpg"},"name":"DEVILMAN crybaby","name_cn":"恶魔人 crybaby","summary":"随着恶魔觉醒，人类世界陷入混乱。性格温柔的男孩与恶魔合体，在神秘好友飞鸟了的指引下，卷入一场残酷、堕落的对抗邪恶之战。","total_episodes":10,"eps":10},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:37:35+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":11577,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2011-07-07","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a8/6a/11577_5U5G1.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a8/6a/11577_5U5G1.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a8/6a/11577_5U5G1.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a8/6a/11577_5U5G1.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a8/6a/11577_5U5G1.jpg"},"name":"THE IDOLM@STER","name_cn":"偶像大师","summary":"　　偶像，是女孩子们一直以来的憧憬。但能站在顶点的，只有仅仅数人。13位少女，就此经她们所属的事务所“765 Prodution”，跨进了那个充满竞争的世界……出道约半年，事务所来了一位全新的制作人。他跟少女们都下定决心，向顶级偶像之路进发…… 本作是由『A-1 Pictures』改编同名游戏于2011年7月制作的最新版动画，讲述了『765production』所属的偶像们活跃与成长的物语。\r\n\r\n　　2011年1月10日，在“The Idolm@ster 2 765pro H@ppiness New Ye@r P@rty!! 2011”的现场活动中，隆重地隆动地宣布了一个使所有fans非常雀跃的消息——「THE IDOLM@STER(偶像大师)」的动画化计划正式启动了! 那时虽然已经宣布了动画化，但是以什么媒传播放则还没有公布，再次TV动画，还是直接剧场版，还是只推出OVA? 这些疑问都在最新一号的「Megami杂志 3月号」上得以解答了，「THE IDOLM@STER」TV动画化正式决定!! ","total_episodes":26,"eps":26},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:36:56+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":18624,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2011-07-07","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/92/f6/18624_ZFj5M.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/92/f6/18624_ZFj5M.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/92/f6/18624_ZFj5M.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/92/f6/18624_ZFj5M.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/92/f6/18624_ZFj5M.jpg"},"name":"輪るピングドラム","name_cn":"回转企鹅罐","summary":"幾原邦彦所监督的原创动画，以高仓家的三兄妹——双子兄弟高仓冠叶和高仓晶马，以及体弱多病的妹妹高仓阳毬为中心展开的故事。\r\n某天兄弟二人带着时日无多的妹妹去水族馆游玩，久未外出的阳毬在人群中忽然倒下气绝。之后在停尸间，在绝望的兄弟二人面前，死去的妹妹又突然戴着企鹅帽子站起来，大喊道“生存战略！”“妾身已为此女续命！”然而当企鹅帽子掉落时，阳毬又恢复成了平常的样子。\r\n靠着不可思议的企鹅帽子，阳毬的生命得以延续。当戴着企鹅帽的阳毬再次出现时，她对高仓兄弟下令道：“去拿到企鹅罐！”","total_episodes":32,"eps":24},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:34:20+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":843,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2004-02-02","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/3d/8e/843_6wj9L.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/3d/8e/843_6wj9L.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/3d/8e/843_6wj9L.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/3d/8e/843_6wj9L.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/3d/8e/843_6wj9L.jpg"},"name":"妄想代理人","name_cn":"妄想代理人","summary":"著名的設計師鷺月子在一天夜裏突然遭到神秘少年襲擊。在此之後接連出現新的受害者，城中一度陷入恐慌。事件的真相究竟是……","total_episodes":13,"eps":13},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:30:59+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":794,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2007-05-12","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/82/48/794_f6jdH.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/82/48/794_f6jdH.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/82/48/794_f6jdH.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/82/48/794_f6jdH.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/82/48/794_f6jdH.jpg"},"name":"電脳コイル","name_cn":"电脑线圈","summary":"西元2026年，被称为“电脑眼镜”的眼镜型透明显示器已经在全世界普及了11年。在电脑内才存在的虚拟宠物、道具、或是互联网都可以戴上电脑眼镜来看到。\r\n\r\n暑假结束时，优子（正确的念法为ゆうこ，Yūko，但通常被称为ヤサコ，Yasako）与双亲还有妹妹京子搬家到大黑市，在抵达大黑市过马路的时候看到了不可思议的事情与在原住地金泽从来没有看过的道具。同时遇见了另一个“ゆうこ”，通常被称为イサコ（Isako）的天泽勇子，以及其他的小孩子们，于是开启了优子在大黑市冒险的日子。","total_episodes":29,"eps":26},{"updated_at":"2020-08-21T08:30:51+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":27364,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2012-04-22","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/cd/38/27364_1ZFmr.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/cd/38/27364_1ZFmr.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/cd/38/27364_1ZFmr.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/cd/38/27364_1ZFmr.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/cd/38/27364_1ZFmr.jpg"},"name":"氷菓","name_cn":"冰菓","summary":"以节能为座右铭的高中生折木奉太郎， 为一个小小的原因而加入了濒临废社的“古典文学部”。古典文学部的社员，包括他在社里认识的好奇宝宝，也就是女主角千反田爱瑠，还有他从国中就认识的伊原摩耶花和福部里志。这是他们四人以神山高中为舞台，对一桩桩事件展开推理的青春学园推理剧。“我很好奇！”奉太郎平静的灰色高中生活，因为千反田的这一句话而为之一变！","total_episodes":26,"eps":22},{"updated_at":"2019-12-14T22:36:26+08:00","comment":null,"tags":[],"subject_id":5658,"vol_status":0,"ep_status":0,"subject_type":2,"type":1,"rate":0,"private":false,"date":"2010-07-02","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/8c/96/5658_xXJX8.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/8c/96/5658_xXJX8.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/8c/96/5658_xXJX8.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8c/96/5658_xXJX8.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/8c/96/5658_xXJX8.jpg"},"name":"みつどもえ","name_cn":"超元气三姐妹","summary":"改编自樱井纪雄的同名漫画作品，《超元气3姐妹》故事以丸井家就读小学六年级的三胞胎姐妹为中心，长女「三叶」是一个稍嫌早熟的虐待狂少女，以女王自居的她，认为所有的人都要对他服从。次女「双叶」是个有点色色的少女，头脑简单四肢发达的她，最喜欢的东西就是女人的胸部。三女「一叶」则是个有点不可思议的阴沉型少女，常被人误认是灵异少女，但是在家中的料理及家事都是由她负责。 \r\n\r\n作品描述不只长的完全不一样，连个性也南辕北辙的三胞胎，在日常生活中与身边的人们所发生的搞笑趣事。 ","total_episodes":14,"eps":14}],"total":15}